==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Elevated
<hw>El"e*va`ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Uplifted; high;
lofty; also, animated; noble; <as>as, <ex>elevated</ex>
thoughts</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Elevated railway</b></col>, <cd>one in which the track is
raised considerably above the ground, especially a city railway above
the line of street travel.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Elevatedness</ent>⟦br⟧
